high_descs: Turn around and exit the bathroom, walk down the path to the lamp, then walk straight ahead to the two doors and enter the one on the right to the bed.
Pick up the knife on the bed.
Turn towards the shelves behind you.
Cut the potato on the bottom shelf.
Look at the shelf again.
Place the knife down on the shelf.
Look down at the bottom shelf with the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Leave the room the way you came in, then turn right, walk ahead a bit and take the doorway on the right into the other room, then left towards the fridge.
Place the slice of the potato in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Leave the room the way you came in, go straight ahead to the wall, then take the path on the left to the bathroom sink.
Place the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Slice a Potato and place one slice into a SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the lamp and turn right to walk into the bedroom to reach the bed on the right.
Pick up the knife from the bed.
Turn around and walk to the shelf.
Cut the potato in the bottom of the shelf to pieces with the knife.
Move right to face the shelf.
Put the knife in the bottom shelf.
Move left to face the shelf.
Pick up a slice of potato from the shelf.
Turn left to exit the room and take a right turn to enter the dining room and reach the fridge on the left.
Cool the slice of potato in the fridge and take it out.
Turn left to exit the dining room and walk up to the lamp and turn left to find the bathroom on the left and reach the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold potato in the SinkBasin.
